draft.title: SMARTYPANTS Funny Dog Christmas Card - Cute Puppy Tangled in Lights Festive Greeting Card for Him Her Men Women - Humorous Animal Holiday Cards with Envelope for Family and Friends
draft.description:
Bring a smile to someone's face this Christmas with this delightfully funny greeting card from SMARTYPANTS. Featuring a charming cartoon dog hilariously tangled in festive fairy lights, it's the perfect way to share a moment of joy and laughter during the holidays. This isn't just any card; it's a small piece of happiness designed for the dog lover in your life.

Crafted from premium-quality cardstock with a vibrant, lasting print, this card feels as good as it looks. The inside is left blank for your own personal message, making it wonderfully versatile. Paired with a stylish, recycled kraft envelope, it's ready to be sent to friends, family, or colleagues to make their Christmas extra merry and bright.

bullets: Charming Festive Design – Spread holiday cheer with this adorable card featuring a happy dog tangled in Christmas lights - the perfect funny greeting for any dog lover this season.
Premium Quality Cardstock – Printed on thick 350gsm cardstock for a superior feel and includes a high-quality recycled kraft envelope for a rustic and eco-friendly touch.
Blank For Your Message – The inside is left completely blank allowing you to write your own personalised heartfelt or hilarious message to friends family or colleagues this Xmas.
Vibrant Lasting Colours – Our professional printing process ensures the deep red background and colourful details are sharp vibrant and resistant to fading for a memorable keepsake.
Send With A Smile – Ideal for sending festive wishes to any man woman friend or family member who appreciates a bit of cute animal humour during the holiday celebrations.
